article_text: The "It's a Jeep thing" crowd doesn't need convincing, but converts will be made by the 2014 Jeep Cherokee. Cars.com reviewer David Thomas was wowed by the all-new compact SUV's "daring design," sophisticated interior, and performance. Cars.com
